text: Bishkain () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Polyakovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 22 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Davlekanovo, 9 km from Polyakovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Bishkain, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
